Configure and evaluate ACLs, firewalls, and zone-based policies

Understand SIEM data sources and alert generation

Classify and triage security alerts

Apply Zero Trust and access control principles

Understand cryptography from a defensive monitoring perspective

Analyze network traffic and common protocols for security relevance

